query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS evaluations (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  candidateId INT NOT NULL,
  evaluatorId INT NOT NULL,
  category VARCHAR(100),
  score INT,
  comments TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
